: 16px 0;"&gt;根据美国气象局发布的一份咨询报告，虽然即将到来的圣安娜风预计不会像上周席卷洛杉矶的风暴那么强烈，但受到警告的地区“将有很高的风险发生大火， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=307da186807b477a8170c737d381c37a&amp;amp;_e=xloyQb76a-ay65Wc1yWUAgmpa5erBn6QBzCV1ZikGeflfsqFdVAaNuU0qQJvNFAhfVv3rbVOeqgeSyHk1pdmv_4IjEP5qhRdyc5Z4LF8AuNwMZNRECX0-r--z9GSaXy0gAsF-3-CnPK0U2O6uCb3is_Bjfge1WW799Le7oqteteSf7A7W8Abeja9LW-PrytldKCB9mUZ5SW4qUaLMTfp9gFQ5yjSSzk6Z2qj6z6UUdQ1WELpJzxh688KXl0o5ZRwslgVXLO4EOQcK3Di8cH-pjNIfGDUKJHv6u5LymKJznnJTEoZT2MqbgbhO6819e2RI9tvu5Z1zuf1b0sMjTW9pGiYRIi5J6Xiu56nTdIMWqYUVQHfJic20HN7HOn2hzA4KxmnEqDpcSr82By4W0VWIbN4nRmPY4UjySrG7T5bNAU%3D" target="_blank" title="国家气象局咨询"&gt;火势蔓延非常迅速&lt;/a&gt;”。国家气象局周日晚间。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;大风将限制消防员在扑灭快速蔓延的 Palisades 和 Eaton 大火方面取得进展的机会，这场大火已造成洛杉矶 Pacific Palisades 和 Altadena 社区至少&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=307da186807b477a8170c737d381c37a&amp;amp;_e=xloyQb76a-ay65Wc1yWUAhJ0X0krDbuXFa3PJuw86ifZsLuleYnyMNfNgXmxqcCO8J3AWVDZbLwJokXXqfdgmy9euBoQSozSyyhsta_SHSXkqwMTVz7XKkhCUNzTzOS_uCGz4qy8iXBHLv3esKfRzAMalIQYpg2WBr8oTUMZcUE5L2iQnKXjOZ1k27eEBEy-P2Hc8GLJFO2Kd_58XnDYGmaxtAkmYj-K7Py3HJbyPqmrBEj03i6jQhyz8wakS0Bwa4b0xkp7cKhhwam1JGLzs1VQpj0g46MSp9PNVGjasOJpzWIOo53k0Nsiem5H0jr7qNmWpm-BBQnABxCBjLSKCA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;24 人&lt;/a&gt;死亡，并烧毁了 12,000 多栋建筑物。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;em&gt;请在 Bloomberg.com 上阅读&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=307da186807b477a8170c737d381c37a&amp;amp;_e=xloyQb76a-ay65Wc1yWUArdRgjflNvDNWDcz2Cu5f6ITYKOXK5gYsoYmXHm4GpAkXxJQoOi4auLqBuopnGfoY-QB7UtDvtSB7xonTHA31eyl5LGia-FBeRieZSiuDY49gJtFNkNhq2ZZ-7wjjau5VE5JvDL91PU97AAVG2utNN-dWfUScVJY9MEE28ppkIAl8jTYrseHgVR9kenZbuj9oNs_WIptcBzvIk08ii6Lu2WTKKaJxTEdOYQjEyku3Qa-lvO0cMTH_Vi_jZ3RjtfGwi1ufKlEj88LdHHV_2FsNod5mtDp0Buhz